    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been a fantastic, reliable companion and is still in really solid shape. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics, so it runs smoothly and looks great parked in the driveway. It\u2019s perfect for someone wanting a dependable ride without the 'new car' price tag. Drop me a message if you'd like to take it for a spin!",
