    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused Porsche Cayman S (987.2) featuring the robust 3.4L 9A1 flat-six engine with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI). This mid-engine platform delivers an exceptional polar moment of inertia, paired with a precise 6-speed manual transmission for tactile gear engagement. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, supported by a well-sorted MacPherson strut suspension and four-piston monobloc calipers for consistent thermal management under load. Mechanically sound with a linear power band and sharp throttle response, this example represents a pure analog driving experience. Recent maintenance includes a full fluid service and cooling system inspection.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
