    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Luxury Sport Sedan is a prime example of a well-loved vehicle that balances performance with daily utility. The Metallic Charcoal exterior retains a brilliant luster, showing only minor stone chips from highway driving that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the premium black leather seats are firm and free of cracks or stains, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system\u2014operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with a fresh oil change, new filters, and a multi-point inspection performed just 500 miles ago. The turbocharged engine provides smooth power delivery, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. Included with the sale are two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a thick folder of service receipts. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for immediate enjoyment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
